{"tid":2156313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方：拒港台進入壹傳媒大樓封鎖區是溝通延誤","createTime":"2020-08-14T10:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T14:05:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a8dc72a38f3528e3a9c5f01f25a94965e67e40ab","tid":2156313,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"記協前日去信警務處長鄧炳強，呼籲盡快取消只安排部份傳媒，進入封鎖線範圍內採訪的新措施。警方回信，提到星期一在將軍澳壹傳媒大樓，拒絕港台記者進入封鎖區內，只是出現溝通和聯絡上的延誤，最終港台記者都順利進入封鎖區內採訪。 <br />\n<br />\n信中又指，當日採訪安排是試行性質，重申希望在不影響行動效能的情況下，增加警務工作的透明度，警方理解傳媒業界有不同意見，會在充分聽取意見後檢討和優化日後安排。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2352504&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=b601247f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352504</a>"},{"pid":"40b28cf839e02e407f48724def7fec5a624ea0fe","tid":2156313,"uid":132587,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6bd2a47dae10b431d6745fb1aedb657df5913be","tid":2156313,"uid":284119,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"算尻數啦 成日做完陰質野又唔撚認 冇閪用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5d1772471244269b6a6f7566150035b5dd0a12","tid":2156313,"uid":81273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"政府部門都唔俾入<br />\n講真港台前線黃真係fc左"},{"pid":"1fe6e4643fa070fbed6886631fdfbeba9de3933b","tid":2156313,"uid":89198,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"含撚啦，做完就扮傻"},{"pid":"04346e1dce93a309997305e81aeef637db7365b1","tid":2156313,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b28cf839e02e407f48724def7fec5a624ea0fe","tid":2156313,"uid":132587,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"cited